nd loving environment to the kids while they receive the therapy and services they need to grow and heal. It was a pleasure to be a part of their mission for a day.</p>\n<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-1400 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-large'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"attachment-large size-large inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:750px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:75%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/20e77/IMG_58182.jpg 188w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/f21ed/IMG_58182.jpg 375w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/88df8/IMG_58182.jpg 750w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/b2f64/IMG_58182.jpg 1125w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/9d81f/IMG_58182.jpg 1500w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/4251c/IMG_58182.jpg 2016w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcSet=\"/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/20e77/IMG_58182.jpg 188w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/f21ed/IMG_58182.jpg 375w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/88df8/IMG_58182.jpg 750w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/b2f64/IMG_58182.jpg 1125w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/9d81f/IMG_58182.jpg 1500w,\n/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/4251c/IMG_58182.jpg 2016w\" src=\"/static/b5825495d8b38e9131e93833e68c3cdb/88df8/IMG_58182.jpg\" alt=\"The PM Group staff at Respite Care\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transit